item.title: double-booked myself
item.description: 02:02 Monday 12 October 2015 JST HI Ken I have just discovered I made the most amazing fuckup imaginable and cannot teach the lesson on Wednesday. I will try to find somebody to cover it. I'm totally embarrassed because I specifically told you that I don't fuck around with my schedule like that, and yet I did. I'm sorry, and I know "sorry" is meaningless. I will help find someone to cover it.
